  "_NOTES": [
    "COMBINED WORKFLOW: E02S01 + E02S02 + E02S03",
    "",
    "TRUE path (tech found):",
    "  Webhook → Respond to Webhook → Parse SMS Fields → Get Client by Phone",
    "  → Client Found? → Extract Tech Name → Get Tech by Name → Tech Found? [TRUE]",
    "  → Get Latest New Job → Job is New? → Assign Job → Build Confirmation SMS",
    "  → Send Confirmation SMS",
    "",
    "FALSE path (tech NOT found — E02S03):",
    "  Tech Found? [FALSE] → Fetch All Techs → Build Error SMS → Send Error SMS",
    "",
    "BEFORE ACTIVATING:",
    "1. Replace SUPABASE_ANON_KEY_PLACEHOLDER in ALL 5 HTTP Request nodes",
    "   (Get Client by Phone, Get Tech by Name, Get Latest New Job, Assign Job, Fetch All Techs)",
    "2. Configure Twilio credentials in n8n — applies to Send Confirmation SMS and Send Error SMS",
    "3. Ensure a job with status=New exists in Supabase for testing",
    "",
    "MANUAL WIRING REQUIRED after import (n8n v2 splitInBatches bug):",
    "  - Verify 'Tech Found?' FALSE output (index 1) connects to 'Fetch All Techs'",
    "    (n8n may re-wire to TRUE output on import — check and correct manually)",
    "",
    "E02S04 hook: connect 'Job is New?' FALSE branch → already-assigned SMS node"
  ]
